root: ^Welcome to your first day at The Astro Parcel Service. To save time, call us TAPS.
^I'm your manager. You can refer to me as Manager.
^I don't care who you are. You'll be zipping around in this job so I'm just going to call you "Zip."
^At TAPS, we provide high quality customer service with each packaged plant delivery.
^But we can't do that if you just stand around all day! Get to work, Zip!
